    "en": {
      "title": "The trio in the children's home escaped",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A complaint has been made at the police station that 3 children who were detained in a children's home in Galle have escaped from there.",
        "It is noteworthy that these three children were sent to the said children's home as per the court order of the Matara Magistrate while they were wandering on the streets."
      ],
